ague]] <small>(2)</small>\n| {{Flagicon|ENG}} {{sortname|Judd|Trump}}\n| align=\"center\"|2\u20133\n|- style=\"background:#ffc;\"\n| style=\"background:#98FB98\"|Winner\n| 3.\n| [[2010 Masters (snooker)|2010]]\n| [[Masters (snooker)|The Masters]] <small>(2)</small>\n| {{Flagicon|ENG}} {{sortname|Ronnie|O'Sullivan}}\n| align=\"center\"|10\u20139\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98FB98\"|Winner\n| 4.\n| [[2011 Wuxi Classic|2011]]\n| [[Wuxi Classic]]\n| {{Flagicon|ENG}} {{sortname|Ali|Carter}}\n| align=\"center\"|9\u20137\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98FB98\"|Winner\n| 5.\n| 2012\n| HK Spring Trophy\n| {{Flagicon|ENG}} {{sortname|Andrew|Higginson}}\n| align=\"center\"|7\u20131\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#ffc;\"\n| style=\"background:#98FB98\"|Winner\n| 6.\n| [[2013 Masters (snooker)|2013]]\n| [[Masters (snooker)|The Masters]] <small>(3)</small>\n| {{Flagicon|AUS}} {{sortname|Neil|Robertson|Neil Robertson (snooker player)}}\n| align=\"center\"|10\u20136\n|- style=\"background:#ffc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up\n| 8.\n| [[2014 Masters (snooker)|2014]]\n| [[Masters (snooker)|The Masters]] <small>(2)</small>\n| {{Flagicon|ENG}} {{sortname|Ronnie|O'Sullivan}}\n| align=\"center\"|4\u201310\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98FB98\"|Winner\n| 7.\n| [[2017 Haining Open|2017]]\n| [[Haining Open]]\n| {{Flagicon|ENG}} {{sortname|Tom|Ford|Tom Ford (snooker player)}}\n| align=\"center\"| 5\u20131\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98FB98\"|Winner\n| 8.\n| [[2018 Haining Open|2018]]\n| [[Haining Open]] <small>(2)</small>\n| {{Flagicon|CHN}} [[Li Hang (snooker player)|Li Hang]]\n| align=\"center\"| 5\u20134\n|}\n\n===Pro-am finals: 1 (1 runner-up)===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:80px;\"|Outcome\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20px;\"|No.\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:50px;\"|Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:200px;\"|Championship\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:200px;\"|Opponent in the final\n! scope=\"col\"  style=\"text-align:center; width:50px;\"|S